cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the telecommunications system providing VoD service, which involves network architecture and protocols. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on video transfer and optimization. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper uses a multi-layer graph to model the system and solve optimization problems. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) could be a possible category as the paper deals with the relationships between structural elements in the system. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the optimal configuration of the system for resource consumption.
